- * given @rate and places them to @chip->div_cpsr and @chip->div_scr. If,
- * for some reason, divisors cannot be calculated nothing is stored and
- * %-EINVAL is returned.
+ * This will write to TX and read from RX according to the parameters
+ * set in lpc31xx.
